      "content": "The Visa Click to Pay API enables merchants and payment service providers to integrate Visa's secure remote commerce checkout experience. Based on EMV Secure Remote Commerce (SRC) standards, Click to Pay provides a streamlined online checkout flow where consumers can pay with stored Visa credentials without re-entering card details for each purchase.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Visa Developer Support",
